Prepare Bob Evans Original Mashed Potatoes by following the recommended microwaving instructions on the package. Mix in 2 Tbsp of prepared horseradish until well combined. Place 6 oz. of Bob Evans Original Mashed Potatoes with horseradish in a martini glass. Top with 2 slices of medium rare roast beef, mounded in the center. Top with 1 oz of au jus. Place 2 Tbsp goat cheese over beef and au jus. Top with 1 tsp. crispy shallots Garnish with fresh snipped chives